Dan Oxenbold,
a partner at the law firm

02:06.294 --> 02:07.895
Oxenbold and Jensen...
Got it!

02:07.928 --> 02:09.506
Was murdered today
on the streets...
Found it, Diane.

02:09.530 --> 02:10.574
Of downtown Chicago.
It's true?

02:10.598 --> 02:11.565
Looks like it.
The gunman

02:11.599 --> 02:12.566
was taken into custody

02:12.600 --> 02:13.801
30 this morning,

02:13.834 --> 02:15.636
after he was caught on camera
in what police

02:15.669 --> 02:18.339
called a targeted killing
in broad daylight.

02:18.372 --> 02:20.941
It was crazy!
I was just on my way to work.

02:20.974 --> 02:22.676
I was walking down the street,
and some guy

