came out of nowhere
and shot him.

02:24.645 --> 02:26.323
The next thing I knew,
he was down...
Oh, my God.

02:26.347 --> 02:27.591
On the ground
and everyone starts running.

02:27.615 --> 02:29.917
Complete chaos.
Again?

02:29.950 --> 02:31.452
Just today.

02:31.485 --> 02:32.886
Well, did they find him?

02:32.920 --> 02:34.655
Randy Fox
recently declared bankruptcy

02:34.688 --> 02:36.624
after losing a hearing
over a patent dispute,

02:36.657 --> 02:38.226
a loss he blamed on his lawyer.

02:38.259 --> 02:39.927
Dear God, it's like a plague.

02:39.960 --> 02:42.396
This appears to be a copycat
of the hit-and-run killing

02:42.430 --> 02:45.299
